---
layout: archive
title: "Writing"
permalink: /writing/
author_profile: false
---

<div class="lh-archive-intro">
  <p>short thoughts, notes, and quiet sentences</p>
</div>

<ul class="lh-archive-writing-list">
  {% assign posts = site.categories.writing %}
  {% for post in posts %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url | relative_url }}">{{ post.title }}</a>
      <span>{{ post.date | date: "%Y.%m.%d" }}</span>
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>